short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Send LinkedIn user profile data straight to Wisnio.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Wisnio's Chrome extension is a game-changer for executive search professionals:
-> Download LinkedIn Profile Information: Easily import LinkedIn profile data into Wisnio.
-> Profile Management: Amend existing candidate profiles or create new candidate profiles with a click.
-> AI-Powered Summaries: Generate detailed summaries of candidates' experiences, skills, and achievements using generative AI.

Simplify your executive search process, making it more efficient and effective with Wisnio's technology.
